# CRUD API Standards

- **Routes**: Use plurals as endpoints. E.g. `/api/v1/sites`, `/api/v1/sites/{siteId}/panels`, `/api/v1/panels/{panelId}/motors`.
- **Performance**: Nutze `TypedResults` für 0-Reflection Metadaten.
- **AOT**: Registriere alle Response-Records im `JsonSerializerContext`.